  branching:
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Wait...
    nextStepIndices: 01000000
  - _Question:
    - This email doesn't sound very urgent.
    _NpcResponses:
    - This email isn't urgent at all!
    nextStepIndices: 02000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Well, we still need to reply to it. It is one of your tasks after all.
    nextStepIndices: 03000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Want me to reply on your behalf?
    nextStepIndices: 04000000
  - _Question:
    - Please do.
    - I'll do it.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Alright, just give me a moment... and done!
    - Oh, okay... Let me know when you're done, I guess.
    nextStepIndices: 050000000b000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - How does this look?
    nextStepIndices: 06000000
  - _Question:
    - Looks good.
    - Actually, I'd rather write it myself.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Great! I'll go ahead and send the email to your boss, and we can cross this
      off!
    - Oh... Let me know when you're done, I guess.
    nextStepIndices: ffffffff08000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Let me know when you're done, I guess.
    nextStepIndices: 08000000
  - _Question:
    - Alright.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Really? You basically wrote the same thing I did.
    nextStepIndices: 09000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Whatever. I'll send this off to your boss, and mark the task off in the notepad.
    nextStepIndices: ffffffff
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Let me know when you're done.
    nextStepIndices: 0b000000
  - _Question:
    - Alright.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Done?
    nextStepIndices: 0c000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Cool. I'll send this to your boss, and cross it off in the notepad.
    nextStepIndices: ffffffff
